    <item>
      <title>报告称国泰航空发动机起火可能造成重大损失</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/cathay-engine-fire-could-have-led-to-major-damage-report-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[初步报告称，本月早些时候，国泰航空有限公司一架航班的发动机在空中起火，起火原因可能蔓延至飞机并造成大面积损坏，对事故原因和故障部件的调查仍在继续。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/cathay-engine-fire-could-have-led-to-major-damage-report-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Sep 2024 06:54:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储降息推动亚洲货币创 14 个月新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/asian-currencies-hit-14-month-high-as-fed-slashes-interest-rates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国联邦储备委员会启动政策放松并暗示今年将进一步降息后，亚洲货币升至一年多来的最高水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/asian-currencies-hit-14-month-high-as-fed-slashes-interest-rates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Sep 2024 06:54:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储利率调整有望推动亚洲资产大幅上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/fed-s-rate-pivot-seen-driving-outsized-gain-in-asian-assets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储转向降息对亚洲资产来说是个好兆头，因为许多亚洲资产的持有量不足，而且与全球其他资产相比，它们拥有更好的盈利前景和更大的从宽松政策中获益的空间。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/fed-s-rate-pivot-seen-driving-outsized-gain-in-asian-assets</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Sep 2024 06:38:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非储备银行准备四年来首次降息，兰特上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/south-african-rand-usdzar-rises-as-central-bank-prepares-for-interest-rate-cut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周四上午，在南非储备银行公布利率决定之前，兰特上涨，预计该央行将自 2020 年 7 月以来首次降息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/south-african-rand-usdzar-rises-as-central-bank-prepares-for-interest-rate-cut</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Sep 2024 05:57:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>汇丰银行自 2019 年以来首次下调香港基准利率</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/hsbc-cuts-key-rate-in-hong-kong-for-the-first-time-since-2019</link>
      <description><![CDATA[汇丰控股有限公司自 2019 年以来首次下调香港主要基准利率，此举可能会影响利润率，同时为这个亚洲金融中心的房主和借款人带来缓解。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/hsbc-cuts-key-rate-in-hong-kong-for-the-first-time-since-2019</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Sep 2024 04:13:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>铜价因鲍威尔降息半个百分点创两个月新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/metals-mixed-after-initial-boost-from-fed-s-half-point-rate-cut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储降息半个百分点，以捍卫美国经济增长和劳动力市场，金属价格随之上涨，铜价也攀升至 7 月中旬以来的最高水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/metals-mixed-after-initial-boost-from-fed-s-half-point-rate-cut</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Sep 2024 03:14:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员追踪风险偏好基调和中东紧张局势，油价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-september-19</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储大幅降息后，风险偏好情绪席卷了整个金融市场，同时交易员关注中东地区紧张局势的升级，油价随之上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-september-19</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Sep 2024 23:40:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储大幅降息后股市加速上涨：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/stocks-bonds-rangebound-as-traders-digest-fed-cut-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于预期美联储降息半个百分点将引导全球最大经济体实现软着陆，全球股市出现上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/stocks-bonds-rangebound-as-traders-digest-fed-cut-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Sep 2024 22:50:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯过境运输协议即将结束，欧洲天然气供应稳定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/europe-gas-supply-solid-as-russia-transit-deal-ends-uniper-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲最大天然气消费国德国的能源公司表示，即使俄罗斯一条重要天然气运输路线即将关闭，欧洲仍有能力在今年冬季维持稳定的天然气供应。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/europe-gas-supply-solid-as-russia-transit-deal-ends-uniper-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Sep 2024 19:48:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
